parameters: Ugh, I can't BELIEVE that I needed to shop HERE.
I usually do all my shopping at MegaMall, but the
ticket dispenser wasn't working, and I won't solve
any puzzles.  I'll be speaking to the manager! \n<Karen>
The commute up here from the city is exhausting...
But the kids like the park, and my wife likes to
shop... I wish we made enough to justify how much she
spends though. *sigh* \n<Ken>

around.  Its just barely newer than the tower
just north of here, believe it or not.  In fact,
I think they were under construction at the same time.
The tower directly north of here always creeped me
out.  A friend of mine told me that his friend told
him that his brother was told by someone he met at
